search_results.title: S&P 500 Rises 0.5% as Tech Stocks Lead Market Rally
search_results.content: The S&P 500 closed higher today, gaining 0.5% as technology stocks led a broad market rally. The index closed at 4,567.89, up 22.34 points from yesterday's close.

search_results.title: Federal Reserve Holds Interest Rates Steady
search_results.content: The Federal Reserve announced today that it will maintain the current federal funds rate at 5.25-5.50%, citing ongoing inflation concerns and strong economic growth.

search_results.title: NASDAQ Dips 0.3% Despite Strong Apple Earnings
search_results.content: The NASDAQ Composite fell 0.3% today, closing at 14,234.56, despite Apple Inc. reporting better-than-expected quarterly earnings after the bell.
